---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - LastRite"
  description="Read the terms and conditions for using LastRite"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[color:var(--color-background)]">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="bg-[color:var(--color-surface-container)] py-12 px-4 border-b border-[color:var(--color-outline-variant)]">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-[color:var(--color-on-surface-variant)]">Last updated: April 15, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
      <div class="space-y-8 text-[color:var(--color-on-surface-variant)]">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing and using the LastRite website and application, you accept and agree to be bound by
            and comply with these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to abide by the above, please do not
            use this service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">2. Use License</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Permission is granted to temporarily download one copy of the materials for personal,
            non-commercial transitory viewing only. This is the grant of a license, not a transfer of title,
            and under this license you may not:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li>Modify or copy the materials</li>
            <li>Use the materials for any commercial purpose or for any public display</li>
            <li>Attempt to reverse engineer or circumvent any security</li>
            <li>Remove any copyright or proprietary notations</li>
            <li>Transfer the materials to another person or "mirror" the materials</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">3. Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            The materials on LastRite are provided on an "as is" basis. LastRite makes no warranties, expressed
            or implied, and hereby disclaims and negates all other warranties including, without limitation,
            implied warranties or conditions of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement
            of intellectual property or other violation of rights.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">4. Limitations</h2>
          <p>
            In no event shall LastRite or its suppliers be liable for any damages (including, without limitation,
            damages for loss of data or profit, or due to business interruption) arising out of the use or
            inability to use the materials on LastRite.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">5. Accuracy of Materials</h2>
          <p>
            The materials appearing on LastRite could include technical, typographical, or photographic errors.
            LastRite does not warrant that any of the materials on its website are accurate, complete, or current.
            LastRite may make changes to the materials contained on its website at any time without notice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">6. Links</h2>
          <p>
            LastRite has not reviewed all of the sites linked to its website and is not responsible for the
            contents of any such linked site. The inclusion of any link does not imply endorsement by LastRite
            of the site. Use of any such linked website is at the user's own risk.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">7. Modifications</h2>
          <p>
            LastRite may revise these Terms of Service for its website at any time without notice. By using this
            website, you are agreeing to be bound by the then current version of these Terms of Service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">8. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms of Service and any separate agreements we may enter into to provide the Services are
            governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which LastRite operates.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4">9. Contact Information</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at{" "}
            <a href="#" data-coming-soon class="text-[color:var(--color-secondary)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-primary)] font-semibold">
              hello@lastrite.com
            </a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- Back to Home -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[color:var(--color-outline-variant)]">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[color:var(--color-primary)] text-[color:var(--color-on-primary)] font-semibold rounded-btn hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
        >
          ← Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
